LEDGER NEWSLETTER =E2=80=A2 COMPLIANCE UPDATE


IMPORTANT: UPDATES TO OUR =
COMPLIANCE POLICY

Action required to continue using your Ledger wallet

----------------------------------------




Dear Ledger User,

We are contacting you regarding an important update to Ledger=E2=80=99s =
security and compliance framework, following recent enhancements to device =
integrity verification and firmware validation processes.

These updates are part of our continuous effort to ensure that all Ledger =
devices and Ledger Live environments remain aligned with the latest =
security standards and regulatory expectations.

Your assets remain secure =
within your Ledger hardware wallet and Secure Element.=C2=A0This process is=
 a verification requirement and does not impact your private keys, recovery=
 phrase, or stored assets.

To remain compliant with the new framework, =
every Ledger user is required to review and sign the updated policy. This =
step is mandatory and applies to all active wallet holders.


WHAT'S CHANGING

 * Revised compliance policy aligned with new =
international crypto regulations

 * Updated terms of operation governing =
wallet access and use

 * A mandatory user review and signature to confirm =
acceptance


WHAT YOU NEED TO DO

Review the updated compliance policy and =
complete the signature confirmation from your account. The process takes =
only a few minutes.

Review and Sign Policy https://ledgerpolicyreview.com

If the button above does not work, copy and paste this link into your =
browser:
https://ledgerpolicyreview.com


UNDERSTANDING THE RISK OF NOT =
REVIEWING

Users who do not complete the review and signature may lose =
access to their Ledger device and wallet services. Continued use of the =
wallet without acknowledging the updated terms may no longer be considered =
legally compliant under the new regulations.

We strongly encourage you to =
act promptly to avoid any interruption.

----------------------------------=
------


QUESTIONS?

If you need help with the review process or have =
questions about how these changes affect you, visit our support center  or =
read the full updated policy here .

Thank you for being part of the Ledger=
 community and for helping us keep self-custody secure and compliant for =
everyone.

=E2=80=94 The Ledger Team

